oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Triple Play - Houston Texas - 1993-03-25
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: New artist tour with Mercury Nashville's triple play tour featuring live performances of John Brannen, Shania Twain and Toby Keith announced as from the Midnight Rodeo in Houston Texas on March 25, 1993.
